Prerequisites:
    - apache ant
    - uh...java

Building:
    - modify build.xml to your liking
    - run: ant deploy

Usage:
    - To set a server command for a particular redstone wire, point to it and type: /redstonehook set <server command>
    - To get the current command issued for a wire, just point and type: /redstonehook
    - To clear a command for redstone wire, point and type: /redstonehook clear
    - To get a list of currently placed command mappings: /redstonehook getmaps
